xxl.core.predicates

Class LessEqual<P>

  • java.lang.Object
    • xxl.core.predicates.AbstractPredicate<P>
      • xxl.core.predicates.BinaryPredicate<P>
        • xxl.core.predicates.Or<P>
          • xxl.core.predicates.LessEqual<P>
  • Type Parameters:
    P - the type of the predicate's parameters.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Predicate<P>

    public class LessEqual<P>
extends Or<P>
    This class provides a binary predicate that returns true if the first given argument is less than or equal to the second. In other words, when argument0 and argument1 are the given arguments, the predicate returns true if (argument0≤argument1) holds.
